24.00	Vicarious_Visions	Vicarious Visions	Vicarious Visions is an American video game developer. The studio was founded by brothers Karthik and Guha Bala in 1990 while both were in high school. Over the past two decades Vicarious Visions has grown from a few friends working in their parent's basement to a leading developer of video game software. During this time, VV has accounted for over 2.5 billion dollars in retail sales and over 40 million units of its software have been sold worldwide.	
